Package com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.server

Contains the Server Service Wrapper components of SitesWrapper.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DAO
    DAO, (Data Access Object) is a non-instantiable utility class which provides static methods for accessing the JDOs (Java Data Objects) in the GAE (Google App Engine) Data-store.
    Email
    Handles in-bound email messages
    EMF  
    GreetingServiceImpl
    The server side implementation of the RPC service.
    HostPage
    Generates a GWT host page based on the parameters passed to the constructor and initializer methods of the inner class HostPage.Builder and the state of the Site, Style, Page and Landing objects in the GAE Data-store.
    HostPage.Builder
    Provides a builder object to be used as a parameter to the HostPage constructor
    PMF
    JDO Persistence Manager Factory Class ensures there is only a single instance of the persistence manager running
    RESTful  
    RpcImpl
    The server side implementation of the Rpc.
